Tiny Tapas place with great music and amazing local neighborhood vibe. Not touristy at all. Had wonderful tapas and great wine for only 17 euro a person. Hipster tapas with great service.Went to quimet quimet first but it was too crowded and I didn't feel like standing and eating. I Was dying to find a place off the tourist track with local character and found this place. Would recommend for small parties with no children.
